data.description: If you're looking for the charm of a quaint small town while still having convenient access to I35, this home is the ultimate choice. As you step inside, you'll discover the roomy open-concept design that seamlessly combines the living area, kitchen, and dining area. The remainder of the main level has two bedrooms and a generously sized full bathroom complete with a relaxing jetted tub. There's no basement, but the easily accessible crawl space offers ample storage solutions. Adjacent to the kitchen, a roomy deck invites you to savor some of Iowa's most splendid sunsets. Don't let this fantastic opportunity slip through your fingers; make this charming home your own today!
